name: Pokemon Pokeballs [Tumblr post icons]
description: Tumblr 'new post' icons for your dashboard. "A Poké Ball (Japanese: モンスターボール Monster Ball) is a type of item that is critical to a Trainer's quest, used for catching and storing Pokémon. Up to six Pokémon can be carried with a Trainer in Poké Balls, while any number of other Poké Balls can be held in the Bag for later use." *
